zonaws.com/web/direct-files/eda7a074e80c93270884eb89fbb2076e/78f57ced-bc6d-4c42-86ac-d5c9317a6799/products_services/translator_working.jpeg" width="auto"><div class="ov"><span>📝 Translation</span></div></div><div class="srv-body"><p>Document translation across English, Portuguese, Chichewa, and Swahili. Legal, medical, technical, and general business documents. Certified translations available.</p><span class="srv-price">$0.09 – $0.13 / word</span></div></div><div class="srv"><div class="srv-img"><img alt="Transcription" height="auto" loading="lazy" src="https://ppl-ai-code-interpreter-files.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/eda7a074e80c93270884eb89fbb2076e/78f57ced-bc6d-4c42-86ac-d5c9317a6799/products_services/person_headphones_laptop_1.jpeg" width="auto"><div class="ov"><span>🎧 Transcription</span></div></div><div class="srv-body"><p>Audio and video transcription including medical, legal/law enforcement, strict verbatim, and QA review. Multi-language capability.</p><span class="srv-price">$1.50 – $5.00 / audio min</span></div></div><div class="srv"><div class="srv-img"><img alt="Subtitling" height="auto" loading="lazy" src="https://ppl-ai-code-interpreter-files.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/eda7a074e80c93270884eb89fbb2076e/78f57ced-bc6d-4c42-86ac-d5c9317a6799/products_services/person_headphones_laptop_2.jpeg" width="auto"><div class="ov"><span>🎬 Subtitling &amp; Dubbing</span></div></div><div class="srv-body"><p>Professional subtitling for video content and dubbing services. SRT/VTT formats. Training materials, documentaries, corporate communications.</p><span class="srv-price">$10.00 / video min</span></div></div><div class="srv"><div class="srv-img"><img alt="Interpretation" height="auto" loading="lazy" src="https://ppl-ai-code-interpreter-files.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/eda7a074e80c93270884eb89fbb2076e/78f57ced-bc6d-4c42-86ac-d5c9317a6799/products_services/conference_interpreter.jpg" width="auto"><div class="ov"><span>🗣️ Interpretation</span></div><